# TC Pipeline — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env or set in Zo Settings → Advanced → Secrets
# 
# These keys are already configured in /root/.zo/secrets.env
# This file serves as documentation.

# TheOddsAPI — primary odds provider (WNBA, MLB, World Cup, NFL, NHL, NBA)
# Business tier: 200K req/month, player props, multi-book, Pinnacle-anchored edges
# Get key: https://theoddsapi.com
ODDS_API_KEY=

# SportsGameOdds — NBA DK lines (off-season until Oct 2026)
# NOTE: WNBA returns 400 at current tier — ESPN handles WNBA DK lines
# Get key: https://sportsgameodds.com
SPORTSGAMEODDS_API_KEY=

# SportsData.io — NFL / CFB / CBB lines + props
# Used for NFL preseason + regular season DK total/spread/ML
# Get key: https://sportsdata.io
SPORTS_DATA_API_KEY=
